<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Calvin Grove outpointed Anthony English to win the vacant United States Boxing 
Assn. junior lightweight title at Moscow during the first professional card 
featuring Soviet boxers. 
</P>
<P>
The Soviets won all three bouts against their American opponents. 
</P>
<P>
