</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082189-0047 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 97343 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 21, 1989, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part 1; Page 1; Column 5; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
