FADLALLAH, MOHAMMED HUSSEIN; FRANCE -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LEBANON; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LEBANON; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
IRAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SYRIA; THREATS 
