(U.S.) -- CONTRACTS; DEFENSE INDUSTRY; GOVERNMENT CONTRACTS; INFORMERS; FRAUD; 
FALSE CLAIMS ACT; UNITED STATES -- SUITS; LOBBYING; GRASSLEY, CHARLES E 
