the Rose Bowl Hall of Fame. Also honored today were the late Ohio State 
University Coach Woody Hayes and the late USC Coach Howard (Headman) Jones. 
Plunkett played in 1971 Rose Bowl. Elliott came to the Rose Bowl as a Michigan 
player in 1948, as returned as Michigan's head coach in 1965. LORI SHEPLER / 
Los Angeles Times 
